itemDisplayName: Deploy a Standard SKU Service Fabric managed cluster with Key Vault virtual machine extension (KVVM)
description: This template takes a minimum set of parameters and deploys a Standard SKU Service Fabric managed cluster with 1 node type with KVVM and managed identity enabled.
